summary: So I slept on it and still want to know- Where the hell is ARYA??? Word is Maisie filmed more than anyone else,  including KIT,...
body: So I slept on it and still want to know- Where the hell is ARYA??? Word is Maisie filmed more than anyone else, including KIT, and not one single S8 picture of her??? I want S8 to be a love song to her and Bran, let them shine to make up for the travesty done to them in the past couple of seasons. If HBO is saving the best for last then they better do right by those 2 Starks, especially my girl Arya.
